    "body": "\r\n\r\nhttps://www.reddit.com/r/neovim/comments/xnp10k/i_didnt_know_i_needed_smooth_cursor_animations/\r\n\r\n> You need to update your guifont settings since the terminal fonts won't look good in GUI.\r\n\r\nCan we set 'guifont' to nice platform-specific defaults?",
